Formloge is on a mission to democratize access to expertise and reduce toil. Our software enables SME's to build micro ERPs to digitally fulfill form intensive needs, at scale.

Forms suck and they are not going away. If you have ever dealt with taxes, immigration or any regulated form-heavy process, you know the pain! We solve for the two main problems- expertise and the laborious nature of forms; these factors lead to errors, terrible experiences and bad outcomes. 

Formloge's AI enabled platform helps build sophisticated and feature rich user interfaces that natively connect with PDF forms and other integrations to deliver powerful solutions. {https://www.formloge.com/formloge-platform/}

Formloge's team is committed to finding opportunities that can leverage our platform to create outsized impact. In partnership with some of the premier experts in law, we are leading the development of a powerful ERP solution for US Immigration that benefits immigrants and lawyers. 

{https://www.formloge.com/usapath/}

Gestão de vencimentos e armazenamento em nuvem, com backup diário; 
Sistema com tela principal contendo informações em tempo real de todos os documentos vencidos e a vencer;
Sistema de rápido entendimento com organização por pastas, similar ao sistema utilizado em desktop e laptops;
Disparo automático (via sistema) de e-mail para documentos vencidos e a vencer; 
Upload e download de forma rápida e em qualquer formato (pdf, texto, excel, mídia, jpeg, etc.);
Busca rápida e inteligente, possibilitando filtrar por nomes, letras, palavras chave, categorias, comentários, tag(s), etc...;
Digitalização de documentos físicos e armazenamento em nuvem, com controle de vencimentos;
Relacionamento de documentos, possibilitando que vários documentos sejam vinculados entre si. Na busca de documento o sistema apresenta automaticamente os demais documentos vinculados;
Organização e preparação de documentos necessários para cadastro no SISPAT Petrobras;
Opção de utilizar fluxo de trabalho para validação dos documentos armazenados no sistema;
Controle de revisões de documentos, treinamentos e procedimentos;
Relatório de controle vencimentos de documentos, treinamentos e procedimentos;
Relatórios de auditoria de documentos e de usuários em atendimento a LGPD - Lei Geral de Proteção de Dados;
Alteração de status do documento para obsoleto, mantendo o mesmo arquivado em nuvem.

Lynx International is a subsidiary of Axed Group S.p.A. and offers services in the automotive sector, in collaboration with the National Sales Companies, in order to provide the sales network with the best solutions.

Lynx International puts at its customers’ disposal twenty-years of professional experience in the automotive sector and its strong know-how of information technology, in order to achieve objectives of business improvement.

Below the main innovative solutions for improving the business of car industry:

- e-check is the solution for the vehicle reception process: it makes possible its standardisation so that each client is guaranteed the same level of service;

- B.I.A., available on a web domain, is the solution that supports the decision-making process;

-Videocom is the solution for direct communication with the client in a single format, with a uniform message and at the moment of deciding;

- The B2B Parts platform is the solution for cutting the time of processing orders and increasing stock rotation, promoting customer loyalty;

- Autodelta 2.0 DMS OnLine is the technologically advanced solution for the modular and integrated management of all the dealer’s procedures;

- Tyre Integration Platform, a solution which creates a single electronic catalogue of tyres, that can be integrated into the DMS in order to standardise and simplify the sales processes.

